      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean and presents nicely, though it does show minor signs of regular use such as small rock chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches. The interior is in great shape with no major wear or odors, and all mechanical systems are functioning reliably as expected for a car of this quality.",
