      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning, showroom-quality gem! This car is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving just as it did the day it left the lot. From the flawless exterior to the immaculate interior, every detail has been meticulously preserved. If you're looking for a vehicle that offers a truly like-new experience, this is the one for you!",
