    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy. The engine runs roughly and exhibits several noticeable fluid leaks that need immediate repair. Externally, the body shows signs of neglect with multiple dents, scratches, and some rust starting to form on the lower panels. The interior also requires a deep clean and repair of the upholstery. This car is best suited for someone looking for a project or for parts.",
