    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape! It handles beautifully on the road and has been kept up nicely over the years. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready for many more miles. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
