    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This unit remains mechanically stout with a recently overhauled VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Handling is sharpened by refreshed suspension geometry and a 25% locking limited-slip differential. This is a mechanically sound example of an analog icon, perfect for the enthusiast who values longitudinal dynamics and high-RPM induction notes.",
      "price": 32500.0,
