    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This thoughtfully maintained vehicle strikes the ideal balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a high luster, complemented by clean alloy wheels and tires with deep tread life remaining. While there are minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with responsible ownership, the body remains straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the upholstery is well-preserved, and all electronic features\u2014including the navigation system, heated seats, and premium audio\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular fluid changes and inspections. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, turn-key example for a buyer who values a documented history of care and a clean, smoke-free environment.",
